    "A significant challenge faced by educational institutions pertains to the amassed volume of data and its optimal utilization to enhance the quality of academic programs [39].",
    "Common AI data mining techniques according to ReviewDiscover Artificial Intelligence (2024) 4:110 | https://doi.org/10.1007/s44163-024-00163-y [34,40,41] include C4.5 algorithms, k-mean algorithms, support vector machines, a priori algorithms, and expectation maximization algorithms.",
    "As posited by [42], classification algorithms such as Decision Trees, Ada Boost, Support Vector Regression, Naive Bayes, and Stochastic Gradient Descent demonstrate a modest predictive capacity for assessing a student's academic success, modeling distinctions among high, low, and failed performance levels.",
